<p>A followup here.   Empire only works if you have the will to dominate.  To crush all dissent. This requires a large amount of evilness.  And no matter how you  sugarcoat your empire, the peons will still resent it. (<a href="http://www.mwscomp.com/movies/brian/brian-09.htm">link</a>)</p>

